sealed the deal.

95
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,240
Come to think of it,

96
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:21,750
Granny Smith was the last one
in her class, too.

97
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:23,790
Huh.
Same with Big Mcintosh.

98
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:27,210
I really don't see how that's
supposed to make me feel better.

99
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:29,920
