the last one in your class

100
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:32,260
to get a cutie mark
runs in the family.

101
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:33,880
"Runs in the family"?

102
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:37,640
"Runs in the family"!

103
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,680
You've got apples
for your cutie mark.

104
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,520
Granny Smith
has an apple pie.

105
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,730
Big Mcintosh
has an apple half.

106
00:04:43,810 --> 00:04:46,940
My unique talent must have
something to do with apples!

107
00:04:46,980 --> 00:04:49,360
Apples, apples, apples!

108
00:04:52,990 --> 00:04:54,900
Apples.

109
00:04:56,990 --> 00:05:00,620
Get your delicious,
nutritious apples here.

110
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:04,540
Delicious and nutritious
and so many uses.

111
00:05:05,710 --> 00:05:08,540
You can eat 'em,
play with 'em...

112
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:12,710
Hey! Watch it!

113
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:16,300
