with her?

166
00:07:15,590 --> 00:07:17,920
Mm-Hmm.
Well, there you go.

167
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,800
Bet you and Twist would have
a great time together.

168
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,880
Now, run along
and find your friend.

169
00:07:22,930 --> 00:07:25,050
