my racket?!

172
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,690
Yeah, I'm sure.

173
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:39,940
Oh, what's up,
Apple Bloom?

174
00:07:39,990 --> 00:07:41,190
So, I was thinking.

175
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:44,660
